        A clean, focused orchestration experience for the modern architect. No clutter, just performance.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-16 flex justify-center gap-8">
        <button class="px-10 py-5 bg-{{ PRIMARY }} text-white rounded-[24px] text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest shadow-2xl shadow-{{ PRIMARY }}/30 hover:scale-105 transition-all">Initialize</button>
        <button class="px-10 py-5 bg-white border border-neutral-100 text-neutral-400 rounded-[24px] text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:text-neutral-800 transition-all dark:bg-neutral-900 dark:border-neutral-800">Learn More</button>
